Package: montecarlo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, udev
Description: Automated driver matching tool
 Montecarlo attempts to brute-force match drivers for generic USB devices
 by iterating through available modules and checking kernel activity.
